-- Three People Killed in Shooting at Southern California Edison Building
-- B y   L y n n   D o a n
-- 2011-12-17T00:39:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-17/three-people-killed-in-shooting-at-southern-california-edison-building.html
Three people died and two were
injured during a shooting at a Southern  California  Edison Co.
building in Irwindale, California, Mike Taylor, a captain with
the Baldwin Park Police Department, said in a telephone
interview.  Two people died at the scene of the shooting and another
died on the way to a hospital, Taylor said from the scene. One
of the people who died at the building was the shooter, who
appears to have shot himself, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lynn Doan in San Francisco at 
 ldoan6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
